				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is a great place to solo or group.  I personally like chain pulling groups, so I found a partner or two (one of them was a Druid) and I had them pull guardians to me nonstop.  It was great, guardian or two, then the guard, and repeat.<br><br>Stone guardians are cake at this lvl (high blue to yellow), guards are the same, and the Iron guardian is just an xp factory (low red, these can be soloed if you have at least 60% mana)<br><br>Also, if you don't mind taking a little bit of dmg, don't use the earth pet.  Use water instead...  Water has less hps, but it gets hit less, it has a decent dd, and you get hit some to raise that defense cap  hehehe. <br><br>This is a great spot, hardly ever camped, and it offers a lot of roleplaying chances.  Also, lots of high lvl charas pass you to go to Lavastorm, and they will often buff you just for killing the DEs. <p></p><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
